data.description: Looking for the perfect 26 acres to build, farm or develop?  This partially tree lined property is beautiful with some rolling hills, small wetland area, and has some city utilities available.  Once a cherished homestead with barn, only the silo remains, awaiting new owners.  Close to schools, expressways for commuting, Dunes shoreline, and so much more.  A remarkable piece of property with many possibilities.
